Comment: 0,0:20:47.65,0:21:00.95,Ristorante,,0000,0000,0000,,casetta dell'orso

Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:11.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I had fun last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:16.95,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,When can I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:20.82,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:25.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Would you look me in the eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:29.96,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,How long are you going to wear that ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:34.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I get it. You still have feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:41.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You said all those nice things to me. It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You invited {\i1}me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:49.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Now hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:00.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We'll be awaiting your next visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:02.58,Ristorante,MV+FV,0,0,0,,Buona notte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.11,0:01:04.39,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Buona notte.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:18.24,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,This mysterious restaurant is on a road just a little ways from the center of Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:44.84,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Well? Gotten used to the restaurant yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:49.31,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Absolutely. I mean, Vito, Luciano, and all of you have been so kind to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.51,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Furio! Teo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:55.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Not often I see you with a young lady in tow. A new staff member?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is Nicoletta. She's apprenticing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.20,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Likewise. And I appreciate your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is Mauro. He owns this stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:09.63,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I always try to come here when we need vegetables, in between deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He's always got some unique things for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:12.70,Ristorante,,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:14.35,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Have any puntarelle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We been sold out for hours. What time do you think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.77,0:03:20.07,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I was just asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey, I told you not to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, do you have a girlfriend, Teo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.19,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Depends who's asking, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.71,0:03:38.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.36,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,He's just shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:47.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:59.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That daughter of mine... Looks like she's got a crush on Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The one with the red hair, right? I saw her at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:11.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I'm not surprised to hear she did, considering she's {\i1}your{\i0} daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:12.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.67,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A good friend of mine's daughter. I treat her like my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.34,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.62,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, I think I heard about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:27.41,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was talking to Claudio about his wedding ring and when he's gonna take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.29,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She may have gotten the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:33.29,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong about it, Gabrielle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:37.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Did he say he's still in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:39.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's decidedly untrue, Olga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He may have had feelings for me when we broke up,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:46.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,but now it's only because he missed his chance to lose the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Now he's stuck in a holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.04,0:04:52.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Olga, you've got a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your afternoon schedule is packed, so please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Fine, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:01.75,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Anyway, let her be. It'll do her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:05.06,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She still has lots to learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:06.68,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Another divorce case today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:09.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm so sick of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Why do relationships have to be so complicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Olga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:15.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,It's tough to be a sought-after attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.44,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Season the vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.25,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,But don't put so much in as to taint the color of the ravioli.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.73,0:05:29.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We're going to serve this as the staff meal, but do you want to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She seems a bit down today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.21,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.47,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She's depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.66,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Uh, wait, Luciano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:59.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's because Gabrielle came by, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:04.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Even if she's your {\i1}ex-{\i0}wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:08.92,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I know it bothers her. Everyone knows she started working here because she has a thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.85,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's all fine and dandy if you want to date a young girl like Vito,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:18.10,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but if you don't, stop being so kind to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Don't get her hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Tonight was another splendid dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Here's a little token of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:32.03,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can't make it next week, unfortunately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:37.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I finally got tickets to the opera in Milan, so I'll be going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.29,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Oh, Santa Lucia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.88,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Table five is ready for their primo course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.02,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:56.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Maybe it's my imagination, but he's been avoiding looking at me since that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:57.98,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Nicoletta, stop daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.70,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Night, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:16.23,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,It's my treat. Let's have a glass of wine at the enoteca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:19.13,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have something to get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.83,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:24.08,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'll take a rain check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:29.89,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Is he avoiding me after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:36.46,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's quite the bargain, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What do you say, a hundred Euro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.27,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're breaking my balls, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:45.65,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Guess it's a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I've been looking for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:52.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What? Your wife is really that young, Vito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:55.32,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes, she's still in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.50,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:59.15,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I met her at my old gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.15,0:08:01.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I was the one who approached her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.89,0:08:04.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,A couple of exercise-freaks, those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.00,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Be careful when you're with him, unless you like muscle pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:11.03,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So, what's it like being married to someone so much younger than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.03,0:08:13.49,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I don't really think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.49,0:08:15.79,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Every day is a lot of fun, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.71,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:25.42,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, Vito... Claudio's ex-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.92,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Buonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:30.77,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Angela, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.69,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Furio's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.99,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,That's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.93,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're Nicoletta, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:45.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My husband told me about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm Angela. Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.19,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,O-Oh, likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So, how's the wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.38,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yes, I think I'll have the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.62,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,This is my lovely bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.47,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:16.77,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone looks so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good night. I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:47.89,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.89,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Ouch. Long day at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:57.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I had dinner with a couple who are a client of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:58.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My shoulders are all stiff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:02.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Say, want to have a glass of wine over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.91,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Maybe next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.26,0:10:08.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'll swing by the restaurant sometime then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.58,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Ciao.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:24.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.07,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Where the heck were you off gallivanting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.23,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Delinquent girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:55.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What's with all these clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:58.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,They're all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You {\i1}just{\i0} bought me some clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I was out shopping and couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.65,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,My afternoon was free, what can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,OK, I'll go put some tea on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You met Gabrielle, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:32.83,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.22,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's a close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I told you to lay off Claudio, right? About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:48.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I won't say anything if you're serious about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.05,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So? Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:17.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I can't tell if my feelings are real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:22.53,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But I do think... Yeah, he's special.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.87,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm happy when he's around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.43,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and I can't take my eyes off of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:37.80,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Your mind is filled with thoughts of him. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's the most exciting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:46.17,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You've got the real thing, so be confident about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:53.84,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,As your mother, I should be telling you to date someone your own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:57.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,However, as a fellow woman, I want to say that love knows no age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:03.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But Claudio's a tough one, so I don't think it'll be easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:11.54,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The other night, I thought that maybe he still has feelings for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:14.88,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Yeah, that might be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:20.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But he just wears that ring to keep the customers at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:24.51,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Hey, what was it like when you fell in love with the owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:27.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Love at first sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.07,0:13:32.37,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Did he used to be really slender and intelligent-looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:36.21,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Nope. He hasn't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:41.60,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He looked like a bear. I fell in love the first time I laid eyes on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.52,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Was he wearing glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:48.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He's got 20/20 vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:51.97,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Don't you have a spectacles-fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:59.18,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,So when he was opening the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:03.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I made him promise to have all the employees wear spectacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.98,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Isn't he such a sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:14.56,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I screwed up once, so I vowed not to fall in love, and tried to focus exclusively on work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.66,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But once I fall for someone, I'm hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:19.44,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I fall head over heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He proposed to me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:29.12,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But he was dead set on not marrying a woman with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.10,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That's why I had to keep you a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:37.08,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He scared me the other day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:42.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He's got a pretty keen sense of intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.48,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Looking at her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.49,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I'm envious, and I feel kinda depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:05.39,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Let's see... Porro and broccoli...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:11.78,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You opened another expensive bottle of wine, Gigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.81,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Every day. Because the owner doesn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not gonna complain about being able to drink good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:19.94,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.33,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.27,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Good food calls for good wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.80,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,A-Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.26,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:05.56,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Just let me know if anything's bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:10.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I know this might seem strange of me of to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:17.58,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Umm, you've been acting a little odd ever since Gabrielle stopped by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:22.00,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, but that's not what I was thinking about right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.11,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:28.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Claudio, you don't have to go out of your way to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.34,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I overstepped my boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.53,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Luciano said the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.38,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That I'm bothering you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:43.87,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,No, just that it's rude to be kind to you if it's not genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,So what were you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:55.59,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,That I'm jealous of the owner's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.32,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,As a fellow woman, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:01.33,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's got both her work-life and love-life under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:04.35,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Everyone here likes her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.86,0:17:10.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I think you've got a lot in common with her, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:16.16,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You're both straightforward and empowered. But also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.02,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She's my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.26,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:27.57,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Keep that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.13,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,The owner doesn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.36,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I actually planned on telling him when I came here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:40.47,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She dumped me at my grandmother's when I was a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:43.45,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,She never cared for me much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.01,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And it was all so she could marry the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:56.92,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,But, it's also because she got busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:02.89,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I get the fact that her work kept her from caring for me until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:10.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,On the other hand, it pisses me off. Forcing me into this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.83,0:18:15.09,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,I feel both jealous of her full lifestyle
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,and even more pissed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:21.71,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My ex-wife works in the same office as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.76,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:31.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,She got busy with work as well and we were fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.79,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,And that's why you split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.64,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We tried to talk about it and ended up divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,We've got a lot in common, us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.64,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,In that we were both cast aside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.61,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:59.43,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Back when we were still together, I could tell from the look on her face how full her life was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:03.95,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Seeing her like that made me feel a little uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:10.09,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,If you ever have any questions, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:13.05,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how much I can bring to the conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.38,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,but if you ever need someone to vent to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.18,0:19:18.69,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,You're such a nice guy, Claudio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.85,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Are you like this to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.93,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,In the spirit of full disclosure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:29.10,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,My real name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:35.73,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Santo Claudio Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.25,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Paradiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:10.14,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Santo Claudio Paradiso...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:15.54,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,Yes. I was often made fun of it as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:20.86,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,No, it means "heaven"! What better name could you ask for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:25.82,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You can talk to me whenever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:29.04,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.40,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,He really does seem like a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.04,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You work too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:56.20,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,After you're discharged tomorrow, want to stop for a drink on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.20,0:20:58.90,Ristorante,MV,0,0,0,,You know, the one he works at.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:00.90,Ristorante,FV,0,0,0,,Sure.
